## When editing

- Prefer registry/hook shapes over new enemy/class/weapon name branches in engine combat framework.
- Keep server ↔ cf-worker parity (`ws-parity.test.ts`).
- Assets/maps/rulebook live in the content git repo (installed under `node_modules/@vtt-core/hellpiercers-content/`).
- Content must not import `@vtt-core/client` via relative paths — use `@vtt-core/client` package exports.
